Hi <%= @recipient.first_name.presence || @recipient.email %>,

The Reputation & Feedback Agent has flagged a <%= @signal_label %> for <%= @restaurant.name %>.

<% content = @artifact.content.with_indifferent_access %>
Signal:     <%= @signal_label %>
<% if content[:stars].present? %>
Rating:     <%= content[:stars] %>/5 stars
<% end %>
Severity:   <%= @severity.capitalize %>
Root cause: <%= content[:root_cause].to_s.humanize %>
<% if content[:suggested_action].present? && content[:suggested_action] != 'no_action' %>
Suggested:  <%= content[:suggested_action].to_s.humanize %>
<% end %>

<% if content[:draft_message].present? %>
Draft recovery message (requires your approval before sending):
---
<%= content[:draft_message] %>
---
<% end %>

<% if @systemic_issue.present? %>
PATTERN ALERT: <%= @systemic_issue %>

<% end %>
Review in back office: <%= @review_url %>

No messages are sent to customers automatically. You must approve and send any response from the back office.
You're receiving this because you're a manager or owner of <%= @restaurant.name %> on mellow.menu.
